    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>cod fillet[s]</strong> to the pan with the juice of <strong>half</strong> the <strong>lime[s]</strong></p><p>Cook for 4-5 min on each side or until cooked through – this is your <strong>chilli-lime cod</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
