    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>charred pepper & roast potatoes </strong>with the<strong> tomato salsa </strong>to the side, and top with the<strong> chilli-lime cod</strong></p><p>Drizzle over any pan sauce and garnish with the <strong>remaining lime wedges </strong>and <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
